utton\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jtn1665702949730.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jtn1665702949730.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jtn1665702949730.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jtn1665702949730\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Support for Unicode in the MQL Connector\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"jtn1665702949730__support_for_unicode_in_the_mql_connector_159853\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Uniface MQL connector can support Unicode. By default, Unicode support is disabled.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jtn1665702949730__p_d53381e1_d53382e1_d53383e1\">MySQL versions 5.0 and 5.1 provide Unicode support through the <code class=\"ph codeph\">utf8</code> and the <code class=\"ph codeph\">ucs2</code> character sets, which support the Unicode Basic Multilingual Plane (BMP). MySQL 5.5 provides a full range of Unicode character sets—<code class=\"ph codeph\">utf32</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">utf16</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">ucs2</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">utf8mb4</code>, and <code class=\"ph codeph\">utf8</code>. For more details about MySQL Unicode support, consult the MySQL documentation.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jtn1665702949730__p_d53384e1_d53385e1_d53386e1\">The MQL connector provides Unicode support for the MySQL <code class=\"ph codeph\">utf8</code> character set, which only supports the Unicode Basic Multilingual Plane (BMP).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jtn1665702949730__p_d53387e1_d53388e1_d53389e1\">You can enable Unicode support by:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jtn1665702949730__li_d24983e1_d24984e1_d24985e1\">Setting the connector option <code class=\"ph codeph\">unicode=on</code>—enables fields with wide-character packing codes (such as W10, SW* ) to be mapped to the <code class=\"ph codeph\">utf8</code> character set. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"udi1665702731005.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/udi1665702731005.html\" title=\"Unicode is an industry standard designed to allow text and symbols from all languages to be consistently represented and manipulated by computers.\">Unicode</a>.\n                        </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jtn1665702949730__li_d24986e1_d24987e1_d24988e1\">Setting <code class=\"ph codeph\">$DEF_CHARSET=UTF8</code>—enables\n            Unicode characters to be used in table names and column names, user names and passwords,\n            the SQL Workbench and the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sql</span> ProcScript statement. It also sets the\n            default character set for communicating with the MySQL Server to <code class=\"ph codeph\">utf8</code>.\n               <div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"jtn1665702949730__note_w3455ab1b5b9b3b7_w3456ab1b5b9b3_w3457ab1b5b9_w3458ab1b5_w3459ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Set <code class=\"ph codeph\">$DEF_CHARSET=UTF8</code> only if the default\n               character set of the MySQL database is <code class=\"ph codeph\">utf8</code>.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jtr1665702874645.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uniface Support for Unicode</a><p>Uniface supports Unicode in the user interface, database storage and retrieval, sorting, case conversion, and data exchange. Uniface uses Unicode UTF-8 encoding for as its internal character set.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bgx1665702950736.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>unicode</a><p>Enable or disable Unicode support in the MQL connector.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azs1665703222737.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$DEF_CHARSET</a><p>Specify the default character set used for storing data in String fields with C packing code.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529042\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529042\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Support for Unicode in the MQL Connector Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Support for Unicode in the MQL Connector The Uniface MQL connector can support Unicode. By default, Unicode support is disabled. MySQL versions 5.0 and 5.1 provide Unicode support through the utf8 and the ucs2 character sets, which support the Unicode Basic Multilingual Plane (BMP). MySQL 5.5 provides a full range of Unicode character sets— utf32 , utf16 , ucs2 , utf8mb4 , and utf8 . For more details about MySQL Unicode support, consult the MySQL documentation. The MQL connector provides Unicode support for the MySQL utf8 character set, which only supports the Unicode Basic Multilingual Plane (BMP). You can enable Unicode support by: Setting the connector option unicode=on —enables fields with wide-character packing codes (such as W10, SW* ) to be mapped to the utf8 character set. For more information, see Unicode . Setting $DEF_CHARSET=UTF8 —enables Unicode characters to be used in table names and column names, user names and passwords, the SQL Workbench and the sql ProcScript statement. It also sets the default character set for communicating with the MySQL Server to utf8 . Note: Set $DEF_CHARSET=UTF8 only if the default character set of the MySQL database is utf8 . Related Links Uniface Support for Unicode Uniface supports Unicode in the user interface, database storage and retrieval, sorting, case conversion, and data exchange. Uniface uses Unicode UTF-8 encoding for as its internal character set. unicode Enable or disable Unicode support in the MQL connector. $DEF_CHARSET Specify the default character set used for storing data in String fields with C packing code. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}